gcaption%3EPeriod%20cramps%20can%20be%20extremely%20painful%3Cp%3EGrace%20Cary%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDoctors%20are%20finally%20starting%20to%20take%20women's%20period%20pain%20seriously.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESome%20doctors%20say%20that%20period%20cramps%20can%20be%20just%20as%20painful%20%E2%80%94%20or%20more%20painful%20%E2%80%94%20than%20a%20heart%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESevere%20period%20pain%20could%20be%20caused%20by%20an%20underlying%20condition%2C%20like%20endometriosis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20women%20around%20the%20globe%20know%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-rid-of-period-cramps%5C%22%3Eperiod%20cramps%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20miserable.%20But%20doctors%20are%20finally%20starting%20to%20validate%20just%20how%20painful%20these%20camps%20can%20be.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202016%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fqz.com%2F611774%2Fperiod-pain-can-be-as-bad-as-a-heart-attack-so-why-arent-we-researching-how-to-treat-it%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQuartz%20published%20an%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20quote%20from%20reproductive%20health%20professor%20John%20Guillebaud%2C%20who%20told%20Quartz%20that%20patients%20have%20described%20cramp%20pain%20as%20%26quot%3Balmost%20as%20bad%20as%20having%20a%20heart%20attack.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20gynecologist%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrjengunter.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Jen%20Gunter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20writes%20a%20popular%20women's%20health%20blog%2C%20took%20that%20comparison%20one%20step%20further%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrjengunter.com%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2Fcomparing-period-cramps-with-heart-attacks-isnt-useful-or-accurate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20period%20cramps%20are%20often%20much%20%3Cem%3Emore%20%3C%2Fem%3Epainful%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmassive-heart-attack-signs-women-flu-symptoms-2023-12%5C%22%3Eheart%20attacks%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20can%20often%20be%20quite%20mild.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20waiting%20for%20terrible%2C%20excruciating%20chest%20pain%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20you%20are%20having%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%20well%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20miss%20the%20heart%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20Gunter%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BHeart%20attacks%20often%20produce%20vague%20symptoms%20or%20mild%20pain%2C%20that%20is%20why%20many%20people%20ignore%20them%20...%20In%20addition%2C%20more%20than%2040%25%20of%20women%20have%20no%20pain%20with%20heart%20attacks.%20It%20would%20be%20dangerous%20for%20women%20to%20think%20that%20a%20heart%20attack%20should%20be%20at%20least%20as%20bad%20as%20their%20menstrual%20cramps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20are%20period%20cramps%20so%20painful%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22889%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22menstrual%20cramps%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F590a3c8d2c835b1e008b468f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECramps%20can%20be%20seriously%20painful.%3Cp%3EMarcos%20Mesa%20and%20Sam%20Wordley%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPrimary%20dysmenorrhea%20%E2%80%94%20the%20scientific%20term%20for%20painful%20period%20cramps%20%E2%80%94%20affects%2050%20to%2090%20percent%20of%20women%2C%20according%20to%20a%202019%20article%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjama%2Farticle-abstract%2F2758078%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJAMA%20Insights%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20half%20of%20whom%20describe%20the%20pain%20as%20moderate%20to%20severe.%20Despite%20that%2C%20the%20article%20said%2C%20painful%20camps%20are%20often%20%26quot%3Boften%20underdiagnosed%2C%20inadequately%20treated%2C%20and%20normalized%20even%20by%20patients%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20cramping%20pain%20is%20caused%20by%20natural%20chemicals%20called%20prostaglandins%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.acog.org%2Fwomens-health%2Ffaqs%2Fdysmenorrhea-painful-periods%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20College%20of%20Obstetricians%20and%20Gynecologists%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20made%20in%20the%20lining%20of%20the%20uterus.%20These%20chemicals%20cause%20the%20muscles%20and%20blood%20vessels%20of%20the%20uterus%20to%20contract%2C%20and%20can%20also%20lead%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.lww.com%2Fgreenjournal%2Fabstract%2F2020%2F11000%2Fprimary_dysmenorrhea__diagnosis_and_therapy.30.aspx%3Fcontext%3Dfeaturedarticles%26collectionid%3D4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estimulation%20in%20pain%20receptors%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20during%20these%20period%20contractions%2C%20pressure%20on%20the%20uterus%20can%20be%20just%20as%20high%20as%20it%20is%20during%20the%20%26quot%3Bpushing%26quot%3B%20stage%20of%20labor%2C%20Gunter%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20if%20you%20need%20an%20analogy%20to%20describe%20period%20pain%2C%26quot%3B%20Gunter%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Buse%20labor%20or%20cutting%20your%20finger%20off%20without%20an%20anesthetic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESevere%20period%20pain%20isn't%20normal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20while%20mild%20discomfort%20with%20periods%20is%20normal%2C%20severe%20pain%20is%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhara%20Simpson%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20gynecology%20and%20obstetrics%20at%20Johns%20Hopkins%20Hospital%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hopkinsmedicine.org%2Fhealth%2Fwellness-and-prevention%2Fperiod-pain-could-it-be-endometriosis%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CMild%2520discomfort%2520with%2520periods%2520may%2Cdon%2527t%2520have%2520their%2520periods.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20interviewed%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Johns%20Hopkins%20Medicine%20and%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bpain%20that%20stops%20a%20woman%20from%20working%20or%20going%20to%20school%20or%20other%20daily%20activities%20is%20not%20normal%20and%20should%20be%20evaluated%20by%20a%20gynecologist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESevere%20period%20pain%20could%20be%20a%20sign%20of%20an%20underlying%20health%20condition%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdo-i-have-endometriosis-2018-2%5C%22%3Eendometriosis%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Fendometriosis-vs-adenomyosis%5C%22%3Eadenomyosis%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fare-period-cramps-more-painful-than-heart-attack-2018-3%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704494585000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659883fa6979d73718210796%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fare-period-cramps-more-painful-than-heart-attack-2018-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Period%20cramps%20can%20be%20miserable.%20While%20one%20doctor%20compared%20them%20to%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%20another%20said%20that%20the%20comparison%20isn't%20accurate%20because%20many%20heart%20attacks%20are%20actually%20mild.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpraderio%40businessinsider.com%20(Caroline%20Praderio)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A964%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fare-period-cramps-more-painful-than-heart-attack-2018-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sam%20Altman%20says%20tech%20world%20'should%20be%20united'%20in%20supporting%20Muslim%20colleagues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Alt