king.%20That%20medication%20is%20manufactured%20by%20Burkett%20Pharmaceutical%20%E2%80%94%20a%20company%20run%20by%20Joe's%20mother%2C%20Judith%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fprince-charles-friend-joanna-lumley-says-the-crown-made-up-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoanna%20Lumley%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWho%20killed%20Maya's%20sister%20Claire%3F%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225365%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Richard%20Armitage%20as%20Joe%2C%20Michelle%20Keegan%20as%20Maya%20in%20%26quot%3BFool%20Me%20Once.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65987bb61c5c7b8c9a0e8f1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERichard%20Armitage%20as%20Joe%20and%20Michelle%20Keegan%20as%20Maya%20in%20%26quot%3BFool%20Me%20Once.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EVishal%20Sharma%2FNetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20the%20Burkett%20family%20had%20been%20knowingly%20pushing%20out%20drugs%20that%20weren't%20safe%20for%20use%20due%20to%20their%20serious%20side%20effects%2C%20falsifying%20drug%20trials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaya's%20sister%2C%20Claire%2C%20also%20worked%20for%20the%20company%2C%20and%20the%20ending%20reveals%20that%20she%20discovered%20the%20family%20was%20withholding%20information%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20their%20medications.%20We%20learn%20Claire%20had%20also%20been%20working%20with%20Corey%2C%20the%20whistleblower%2C%20to%20gather%20information%20on%20the%20company%20before%20her%20death%20%E2%80%94%20in%20exchange%20for%20Corey%20not%20releasing%20audio%20he%20had%20of%20Maya%20admitting%20to%20killing%20those%20civilians%20when%20she%20was%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViewers%20learn%20that%20Joe%20killed%20Claire%20to%20try%20and%20keep%20the%20company's%20name%20clean%2C%20and%20to%20protect%20the%20family's%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWho%20killed%20Joe%20Burkett%3F%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221067%5C%