%2Fi.insider.com%2F65987c276979d73718210422%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETurns%20out%20Joe%20super%20deserved%20getting%20killed%20by%20his%20wife.%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFlashbacks%20to%201996%20show%20that%20Joe%2C%20his%20brother%20Andrew%2C%20and%20their%20friends%20killed%20a%20schoolmate%20named%20Theo%20Mara%20during%20a%20hazing.%20They%20got%20away%20with%20it%20by%20saying%20Theo's%20death%20was%20accidental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20later%20felt%20guilty%20about%20their%20part%20in%20the%20crime%20and%20wanted%20to%20confess%2C%20but%20Joe%20killed%20him%20during%20a%20confrontation%20on%20a%20yacht%20before%20he%20could.%20Years%20later%2C%20Joe%20also%20killed%20Tommy%20Dark%2C%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20yacht%20who%20witnessed%20Andrew's%20death%2C%20to%20keep%20his%20past%20crimes%20a%20secret.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESo%20wait%2C%20how%20did%20Joe%20Burkett%20show%20up%20on%20the%20nanny%20cam%20if%20he%20really%20was%20dead%3F%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221819%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Richard%20Armitage%20as%20Joe%20Burkett%20in%20%26quot%3BFool%20Me%20Once.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6598470cec62ab5daf8123bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221364%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERichard%20Armitage%20as%20Joe%20Burkett%20in%20%26quot%3BFool%20Me%20Once.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20good%20Coben%20series%2C%20the%20answer%20to%20the%20mystery%20is%20never%20straightforward.%20At%20the%20show's%20start%2C%20Maya's%20nanny%2C%20Izabella%20(Natalia%20Kostrzewa)%2C%20deletes%20the%20video%20of%20Joe%20in%20the%20family's%20home%20and%20then%20feigns%20ignorance%20about%20it%20to%20Maya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20until%20the%20end%20of%20episode%20seven%20that%20Izabella%20and%20her%20husband%20Luka%20(Frederick%20Szkoda)%20admit%20to%20a%20gun-toting%20Maya%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-deepfake%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey%20deepfaked%20the%20video%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20was%20never%20really%20there%3B%20it%20was%20Luka%20standing%20in%20for%20Maya's%20dead%20husband%20with%20some%20added%20technical%20wizardry%20over%20the%20top.%20But%20why%20go%20to%20all%20that%20effort%3F%20Well%2C%20it%20all%20comes%20down%20to%20Maya's%20frosty%20relationship%20with%20her%20mother-in-law%2C%20Judith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJudith%20believed%20that%20Maya%20has%20something%20to%20do%20with%20her%20son's%20murder%20in%20the%20park%2C%20largely%20because%20she%20knew%20her%20own%20son%20was%20Claire's%20killer.%20To%20figure%20out%20what%20happened%2C%20she%20paid%20Izabella%20to%20make%20the%20video%20to%20try%20and%20destabilize%20Maya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20happened%20to%20Maya%20in%20the%20end%3F%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221779%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joanna%20Lumley%20as%20Judith%20Burkett%20and%20Michelle%20Keegan%20as%20Maya%20Stern%20in%20%26quot%3BFool%20Me%20Once.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659847bdec62ab5daf812400%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoanna%20Lumley%20as%20Judith%20Burkett%20and%20Michelle%20Keegan%20as%20Maya%20Stern%20in%20%26quot%3BFool%20Me%20Once.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Maya%20got%20justice%20for%20Claire's%20murder%20by%20killing%20Joe%2C%20she%20also%20wants%20to%20make%20sure%20her%20mother-in-law%20pays%20the%20price%20for%20being%20complicit%20in%20Claire's%20murder%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20damage%20caused%20by%20Burkett%20Pharmaceutical's%20dodgy%20medication.%20(Inexplicably%2C%20Detective%20Kierce%20let%20her%20go%20have%20this%20confrontation%20even%20after%20finding%20out%20Maya%20had%20killed%20Joe%2C%20instead%20of%20just%20arresting%20her.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20so%2C%20Maya%20confronts%20her%20in-laws%20at%20their%20home%20with%20a%20gun%20and%20gets%20them%20to%20confess%20everything.%20It's%20a%20triumphant%20moment%20for%20Maya%2C%20as%20she%20turns%20the%20tables%20on%20her%20entitled%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20Joe's%20other%20brother%2C%20Neil%20(James%20Northcote)%2C%20steals%20Maya's%20gun%20and%20shoots%20her%20several%20times%20in%20the%20chest%2C%20killing%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Maya%20has%20one%20final%20surprise%3A%20She'd%20set%20up%20a%20nanny%20cam%20livestreaming%20the%20whole%20confrontation%20to%20the%20world%20via%20Corey%20the%20Whistle.%20The%20Burketts%20effectively%20confess%20to%20all%20their%20wrongdoings%2C%20and%20they're%20left%20to%20face%20the%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20show's%20final%20few%20minutes%2C%20it%20skips%20ahead%2018%20years%20to%20show%20how%20Maya's%20daughter%2C%20Lily%2C%20was%20raised%20by%20her%20extended%20family%20to%20grow%20up%20happy%20and%20away%20from%20the%20drama%20of%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20even%20has%20a%20baby%20girl%20of%20her%20own%20who%20she%20names%20(you%20guessed%20it)%20Maya.%20Cute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-fool-me-once-ending-explained-who-killed-joe-burkett-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704493053000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659849b7ec62ab5daf812534%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-fool-me-once-ending-explained-who-killed-joe-burkett-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFool%20Me%20Once%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20latest%20Netflix%20series%20from%20mystery%20writer%20Harlan%20Coben%20about%20a%20grieving%20widow%20who%20sees%20her%20dead%20husband%20on%20a%20nanny%20cam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ejacobs%40insider.co