re%20on%20the%20road%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20simple%20trade-off%20for%20convenience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20filled%2C%20the%20Sand%20Kettlebells%20feature%20a%20comfortable%20handle%20that%20makes%20them%20easy%20to%20hold%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20long%20workout.%20They're%20also%20durably%20designed%20and%20able%20to%20be%20used%20on%20gym%20flooring%20but%20also%20on%20cement%20or%20blacktop%20without%20worry%20of%20any%20damage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20they%20do%20feel%20different%20than%20a%20traditional%20kettlebell%2C%20I%20got%20used%20to%20them%20quite%20quickly.%20They're%20certainly%20a%20change%20of%20pace%20but%20not%20so%20much%20so%20that%20they%20ever%20felt%20like%20a%20step%20down%20or%20a%20worse%20alternative.%20Rather%2C%20they're%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20pieces%20of%20fitness%20equipment%20to%20travel%20with%20and%20function%20like%20legit%20kettlebells.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20adjustable%3A%20Bowflex%20SelectTech%20840%20Kettlebell%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221182%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20doing%20side%20to%20side%20crunches%20in%20their%20living%20room%20with%20a%20Bowflex%20SelectTech%20840%20Kettlebell.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e8635c6671de0361c1d453e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22887%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBowflex%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESix%20weights%20in%20one%2C%20affordable%20compared%20to%20buying%20all%20six%20weights%2C%20easy%20to%20adjust%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EExpensive%2C%20handle%20is%20less%20ergonomic%20than%20others%2C%20bulky%2C%20especially%20for%20use%20at%20a%20lighter%20weight%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20%24149%20is%20a%20lot%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20kettlebell.%20But%20with%20the%20Bowflex%20SelectTech%20840%2C%20you're%20getting%20six%20kettlebells%20in%20one%2C%20which%20turns%20this%20into%20quite%20the%20de