22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERick%20Stella%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPremium%20design%2C%20made%20of%20high-grade%20iron%2C%20eye-catching%20color%20coats%2C%20features%20a%20stable%2C%20wide%20base%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EExpensive%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20these%20kettlebells%20from%20Eleiko%20are%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BCompetition%20Set%2C%26quot%3B%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20any%20sort%20of%20competing%20weightlifter%20to%20use%20them.%20They%20%3Cem%3Eare%3C%2Fem%3E%20designed%20and%20calibrated%20for%20competitive%20use%20but%20they're%20just%20as%20useful%20for%20the%20at-home%20lifter%20as%20they%20are%20for%20someone%20you%20might%20see%20on%20ESPN%20throwing%20weights%20around.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20kettlebell%20is%20made%20of%20high-grade%20iron%20(aka%20they're%20indestructible)%20and%20features%20an%20easy-to-grip%20steel%20handle%20that's%20comfortable%20regardless%20of%20the%20exercises%20I'd%20use%20them%20for.%20And%20again%2C%20for%20the%20competitive%20crowd%2C%20this%20also%20means%20that%20they're%20great%20for%20using%20chalk%20with%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20I%20test%20kettlebells%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Collage%20of%20the%20best%20kettlebells%20of%202023%20on%20a%20dark%20orange%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F604a81849942cf001865de3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3B%20Everlast%3B%20Gilbert%20Espinoza%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20the%20various%20kettlebells%20featured%20in%20this%20guide%2C%20I%20spent%20at%20least%20two%20weeks%20with%20each%20pair%20(or%20set)%20to%20gauge%20how%20well%20they%20integrated%20into%20my%20existing%20fitness%20routine.%20This%20meant%20tailoring%20specific%20workouts%20around%20the%20kettlebells%20and%20judging%20what%20they%20were%20like%20to%20use%20based%20on%20these%20four%20categories%3A%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EDesign%2C%20versatility%2C%20comfort%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Evalue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20I%20considered%20each%20category%20while%20testing%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%3A%20Even%20though%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20kettlebells%20are%20immediately%20recognizable%20because%20of%20their%20unique%20shape%2C%20the%20design%20of%20different%20brands%20of%20kettlebells%20does%20differ.%20When%20testing%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20how%20large%20the%20handle%20area%20was%2C%20whether%20the%20round%20part%20of%20the%20weight%20was%20obtrusive%20during%20certain%20routines%2C%20and%20if%20they%20had%20a%20base%20that%20made%20them%20easy%20to%20pick%20up%20and%20set%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVersatility%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20sort-of%20offshoot%20of%20the%20category%20above%2C%20versatility%20as%20it%20relates%20to%20kettlebells%20comes%20down%20to%20whether%20its%20shape%2C%20handle%2C%20and%20base%20allow%20for%20more%20than%20just%20a%20conventional%20workout%20routine.%20I%20tested%20this%20by%20trying%20a%20variety%20of%20different%20handholds%2C%20lifts%2C%20and%20movements%20with%20each%20model.%20The%20kettlebells%20featured%20may%20excel%20in%20their%20specific%20categories%20but%20they%20each%20were%20versatile%20enough%20for%20a%20range%20of%20exercise%20types%20and%20users.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20the%20kettlebell%20you%20use%20doesn't%20feel%20good%20to%20hold%2C%20you'll%20be%20less%20inclined%20to%20want%20to%20do%20a%20kettlebell%20routine%20%E2%80%94%20plain%20and%20simple.%20Testing%20for%20this%20category%20was%20a%20straightforward%20process%2C%20too%3A%20Does%20the%20kettlebell's%20handle%20feel%20comfortable%20in%20hand%3F%20If%20the%20answer%20was%20yes%2C%20even%20at%20the%20tail%20end%20of%20a%20grueling%20workout%2C%20then%20it%20aced%20this%20section.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EValue%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EQuality%20at-home%20workout%20equipment%20often%20comes%20with%20a%20premium%20price%2C%20and%20kettlebells%20are%20no%20different.%20When%20judging%20value%2C%20I%20tended%20to%20consider%20not%20just%20a%20kettlebell's%20sticker%20price%20but%20also%20its%20longevity%20and%20durability.%20It's%20always%20better%20to%20spend%20a%20little%20more%20on%20something%20designed%20to%20last%20than%20to%20spend%20less%20money%20more%20often.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQs%3Ch3%3EWhat%20weight%20of%20kettlebell%20should%20a%20beginner%20buy%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20solid%20foundation%20of%20muscle%20mass%20already%20or%20experience%20using%20a%20kettlebell%2C%20aim%20for%20a%2020-%20to%2025-pound%20(12kg)%20kettlebell%20for%20a%20female%2C%20and%20a%2030-%20to%2035-pound%20(16kg)%20bell%20for%20a%20male.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EFor%20those%20experienced%20with%20a%20kettlebell%20(i.e.%2C%20have%20been%20using%20one%201-2%20times%20a%20week%20already)%2C%20females%20should%20opt%20for%20a%2030-%20to%2045-pound%20(16%20or%2020kg)%20bell%2C%20males%20for%2040-%20to%2050-pound%20(20%20to%2024kg)%20kettlebell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20kind%20of%20workouts%20can%20you%20use%20a%20kettlebell%20for%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKettlebells%20are%20best%20used%20for%20power%20movements%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Cincotta.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20use%20them%20for%20squats%20and%20swings%2C%20and%20you'll%20use%20them%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20single-sided%20exercises%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20asymmetrical%20movements.%20You%20can%20even%20use%20kettlebells%20for%20stability%20work%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20a%20kettlebell%20harder%20to%20use%20than%20a%20dumbbell%20lies%20in%20its%20shape%2C%20which%20puts%20the%20weight%20several%20inches%20away%20from%20your%20hand.%20This%20means%20you'll%20need%20to%20activate%20more%20of%20your%20muscles%20as%20you%20stabilize%20the%20weight.%20With%20a%20kettlebell%2C%20every%20single-handed%20exercise%20like%20curls%2C%20shoulder%20presses%2C%20snatches%2C%20and%20so%20on%20is%20that%20much%20more%20productive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20there%20a%20significant%20injury%20risk%20with%20buying%20a%20kettlebell%20that's%20too%20heavy%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20to%20this%20is%20both%20yes%20and%20no.%20Using%20a%20heavier%20kettlebell%20will%20lead%20to%20more%20results%20because%20you'll%20have%20to%20work%20harder%20to%20move%20it%20and%20therefore%20use%20more%20muscle.%20Keep%20in%20mind%2C%20however%2C%20that%20%26quot%3Bheavier%26quot%3B%20is%20entirely%20relative.%20As%20Cincotta%20mentioned%20(and%20any%20trainer%20will%20tell%20you)%2C%20a%20weight%20above%20your%20strength%20level%20is%20the%20fast%20track%20to%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20can%20I%20correct%20my%20form%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20using%20kettlebells%2C%20safety%20is%20the%20first%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Cincotta.%20%26quot%3BMany%20people%20just%20start%20swinging%20them%20around%20and%20don't%20focus%20on%20form.%20There's%20such%20a%20dynamic%20difference%20using%20them%20%5Bcompared%20to%20other%20weights%5D%20that%20you%20need%20to%20learn%20form%20first.%20And%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20go%20too%20heavy%20too%20quickly%3B%20that's%20a%20very%20easy%20way%20to%20get%20injured.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWith%20that%20advice%20in%20mind%2C%20we%20tested%20a%20variety%20of%20kettlebells%20from%20brands%20like%20Everlast%2C%20TRX%2C%20and%20Bowflex%20to%20find%20the%20best%20currently%20available.%20So%2C%20no%20matter%20if%20you're%20just%20looking%20for%20a%20set%20to%20round%20out%20your%20home%20gym%20or%20want%20to%20kick%20your%20weekly%20fitness%20routine%20up%20a%20few%20notches%2C%20there's%20a%20set%20of%20kettlebells%20perfect%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20many%20types%20of%20kettlebells%20are%20there%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20different%20types.%20Some%20are%20made%20of%20iron%20while%20others%20feature%20a%20vinyl%20coating%20or%20are%20made%20of%20Cordura%20fabric.%20They%20also%20come%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20weight%20options%2C%20mostly%20listed%20as%20kilograms%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20most%20popular%20kettlebell%20size%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20depends%20on%20what%20you%20want%20to%20use%20it%20for.%20Kettlebells%20are%20available%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20weight%20options%20from%20anywhere%20around%208%20kg%20to%20up%20to%2032%20kg%20and%20above.%20Different%20weights%20are%20best%20used%20for%20different%20exercises%20and%20no%20one%20kettlebell%20is%20best%20for%20every%20kind%20of%20workout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fbest-kettlebells%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704490736000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63939548da18750018f1e644%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fbest-kettlebells%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kettlebells%20offer%20a%20strength%2C%20cardio%2C%20and%20flexibility%20workout%20in%20one%20package%2C%20and%20are%20great%20additions%20to%20anyone's%20home%20gym%20setup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rstella%40businessinsider.com%20(Rick%20Stella)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fbest-kettlebells%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reema%20Sen's%20rare%20family%20picture%20goes%20viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704490627000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106583883%2Cimgsize-39268.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fboll