ced%20to%2012%20years.%20In%20this%20view%20of%20the%20matter%2C%20I%20deem%20it%20appropriate%20to%20reduce%20the%20sentence%20of%20the%20appellant%20from%2020%20to%2012%20years.%20The%20fine%20of%20Rs%2015%2C000%20awarded%20by%20the%20trial%20court%20is%20retained.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appellant%2C%20the%20brother-in-law%20of%20the%20survivor's%20tutor%2C%20was%20awarded%20a%2020-year%20jail%20term%20in%202021%20under%20Section%206%20(aggravated%20penetrative%20sexual%20assault)%20of%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act%20and%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20along%20with%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2015%2C000%20by%20the%20trial%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20stated%20that%20under%20POCSO%20Act%2C%20penetrative%20sexual%20assault%20can%20occur%20if%20there%20is%20insertion%2C%20to%20any%20extent%2C%20of%20an%20object%20or%20body%20part%20of%20an%20accused%20into%20the%20vagina%2C%20urethra%2C%20or%20anus%20of%20a%20child%20and%20in%20the%20present%20case%2C%20the%20appellant%20failed%20to%20successfully%20rebut%20the%20%26quot%3Bpresumption%26quot%3B%20against%20him%20by%20leading%20evidence%20or%20discrediting%20the%20evidence%20of%20the%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPenetrative%20sexual%20assault%20qualifies%20as%20aggravated%20penetrative%20sexual%20assault%20under%20certain%20situations%20such%20as%20the%20survivor%20being%20less%20than%2012%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20trial%20court%20rightly%20held%20that%20just%20because%20the%20defence%20witness%2C%20the%20tuition%20teacher%20who%20was%20related%20to%20the%20appellant%2C%20turned%20hostile%2C%20the%20statements%20of%20the%20child%20cannot%20be%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbsence%20of%20external%20injuries%20on%20the%20private%20parts%20as%20well%20as%20the%20hymen%20of%20the%20survivor%20being%20intact%20did%20not%20mean%20that%20she%20was%20not%20subjected%20to%20penetrative%20sexual%20assault%2C%20opined%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20observed%20that%20there%20was%20no%20straight-jacket%20formula%20under%20the%20criminal%20law%20for%20sentencing%20an%20accused%20and%20its%20objective%20should%20be%20to%20create%20a%20deterrence%20as%20well%20as%20bring%20a%20reformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%20that%20the%20appellant%20has%20undergone%20more%20than%20nine%20years%20in%20prison%2C%20during%20which%20he%20has%20been%20working%20as%20a%20'langar%20sahayak'%20and%20his%20conduct%20was%20satisfactory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20not%20been%20involved%20in%20any%20other%20offence.%20It%20is%20also%20relevant%20to%20note%20that%20the%20appellant%20was%20a%20young%20man%20of%20around%2028%20years%20at%20the%20time%20of%20commission%20of%20the%20offence.%20As%20on%20date%2C%20he%20is%20around%2038%20years%20of%20age%20and%20has%20a%20substantial%20life%20ahead%20of%20him.%20He%20also%20has%20an%20aging%20mother%20to%20look%20after%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704477900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Fatt9hsso_court-generic_625x300_27_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-reduces-jail-term-of-man-convicted-for-digital-rape-of-minor-4807769%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20on%20Friday%20reduced%20to%2012%20years%20the%2020-year%20jail%20term%20awarded%20to%20a%20man%20convicted%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20rape%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20four-year-old%20girl%20in%202014.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-reduces-jail-term-of-man-convicted-for-digital-rape-of-minor-4807769%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-reduces-jail-term-of-man-convicted-for-digital-rape-of-minor-4807769%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-high-court-reduces-jail-term-of-man-convicted-for-digital-rape-of-minor-4807769%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20Closed%20Window%20Of%20Vulnerability%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%20On%20Article%20370%20Abrogation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20take%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20(UNSC)%20in%201948%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bfundamental%20error%26quot%3B%20and%20by%20abrogating%20Article%20370%2C%20India%20closed%20a%20'window%20of%20vulnerability'%20which%20New%20Delhi%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bfoolish%20enough%26quot%3B%20to%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20at%20that%20time%2C%20India%20had%20a%20view%20of%20UN%20Security%20Council%20as%20a%20neutral%20arbiter%20while%20a%20set%20of%20countries%20with%20their%20%26quot%3Bgeo-political%20agenda%26quot%3B%20used%20Kashmir%20as%20an%20issue%20of%20%26quot%3Bvulnerability%26quot%3B%20for%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EAM%20was%20speaking%20on%20his%20book%20'Why%20Bharat%20Matters'%20with%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leader%20Tejasavi%20Surya%20at%20the%20Golden%20Jubilee%20Celebration%20of%20PES%20University%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20it%20is%20very%20clear%2C%20in%20fact%20not%20now%2C%20it%20was%20very%20clear%20by%201970s%2C%20that%20taking%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20to%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20was%20a%20fundamental%20error%20because%20you%20are%20taking%20it%20at%20the%20court%20where%20the%20judges%20are%20all%20stacked%20against%20you.%20These%20were%20Western%20countries%20who%20had%20a%20bias%20towards%20Pakistan%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20if%20India%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bhard-headed%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20wouldn't%20have%20made%20that%20'misreading'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BActually%2C%20if%20we%20had%20been%20hard-headed%2C%20if%20we%20had%20a%20good%20sense%20of%20international%20politics%20at%20that%20stage%2C%20we%20would%20not%20have%20taken%20that%20call.%20It%20was%20done%20as%20a%20misreading%20of%20what%20the%20world%20was%20about.%20Somewhere%20we%20saw%20there%20is%20a%20sanctity%20about%20UN...these%20chaps%20will%20be%20impartial%20and%20neutral%20arbiters%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EAM%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20further%20said%20Article%20370%20had%20profound%20implications%20not%20just%20within%20the%20country%20but%20also%20on%20country's%20foreign%20policy%20and%20it%20took%20India%20decades%20to%20finally%20abrogate%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20taken%20in%20for%20a%20ride%20by%20a%20set%20of%20countries%20who%20had%20their%20geo-political%20agenda%2C%20who%20used%20Kashmir%20as%20an%20issue%20of%20vulnerability%20for%20us%20and%20they%20continue%20to%20use%20it.%20It%20took%20us%20decades%20to%20finally%20take%20the%20call%20on%20Article%20370.%20To%20me%2C%20Article%20370%20was%20not%20just%20the%20call%20within%20the%20country...it%20actually%20has%20profound%20foreign%20policy%20implications.%20We%20closed%20today%20a%20window%20of%20vulnerability%20which%20we%20were%20foolish%20enough%20to%20open%20in%201948%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaying%20emphasis%20on%20young%20people%20visiting%20places%20having%20strong%20historical%20cultural%20imprints%2C%20the%20EAM%20said%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20across%20the%20world%20will%20be%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20inauguration%20of%20Ram%20Mandir%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20for%20young%20people%20and%20those%20who%20travel%20abroad%20to%20go%20to%20those%20places