%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fthe-sound-of-music-music-creators-in-india-fail-to-hit-the-right-note-124010501398_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fthe-sound-of-music-music-creators-in-india-fail-to-hit-the-right-note-124010501398_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fthe-sound-of-music-music-creators-in-india-fail-to-hit-the-right-note-124010501398_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'800-Strong%20Mob%20Intended%20To%20Cause%20Death'%3A%20Probe%20Agency%20On%20Bengal%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGiving%20chilling%20details%20about%20the%20attack%20on%20its%20officials%2C%20allegedly%20by%20supporters%20of%20a%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20said%20the%20mob%20consisted%20of%20800-1%2C000%20people%20and%20that%20there%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bintention%20to%20cause%20death%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20three%20of%20its%20officials%20were%20severely%20injured%20and%20that%20people%20in%20the%20mob%20robbed%20its%20personnel%20of%20their%20belongings%2C%20including%20mobile%20phones%2C%20wallets%20and%20laptops.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20occurred%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%20on%20Friday%2C%20when%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20team%20-%20accompanied%20by%20personnel%20from%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF)%20-%20was%20carrying%20out%20searches%20at%20three%20premises%20belonging%20to%20Trinamool%20leader%20Sahajahan%20Sheikh%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20Public%20Distribution%20Scam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20called%20the%20incident%20%26quot%3Ba%20BJP%20conspiracy%26quot%3B%20and%20claimed%20%26quot%3Bunruly%20elements%20attached%20with%20the%20central%20agencies%20provoked%20locals%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20dubbed%20the%20continuance%20of%20the%20ruling%20party's%20government%20in%20the%20state%20%26quot%3Ba%20threat%20to%20national%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20called%20Sheikh%20a%20convenor%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20one%20of%20the%20premises%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20team%20with%20CRPF%20personnel%20was%20attacked%20by%20800-1000%20people%20with%20an%20intention%20to%20cause%20death%20as%20these%20people%20were%20carrying%20weapons%20such%20as%20lathis%2C%20stones%20%26amp%3B%20bricks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20incident%2C%20three%20ED%20officials%20have%20been%20grievously%20injured.%20Injured%20ED%20officials%20are%20being%20admitted%20to%20hospital%20for%20treatment.%20Violent%20mob%20also%20snatched%2Frobbed%2Fstole%20personal%2Fofficial%20belongings%20of%20ED%20officials%20such%20as%20their%20mobile%20phones%2C%20laptop%2C%20cash%2C%20wallets%2C%20etc.%20and%20badly%20damaged%20some%20of%20the%20ED%20vehicles%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20Sheikh%20refused%20to%20unlock%20the%20door%20and%20while%20the%20team%20was%20trying%20to%20get%20it%20open%2C%20the%20mob%20gathered%20within%20half%20an%20hour.%20It%20alleged%20that%20stones%20were%20also%20thrown%20at%20the%20personnel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOther%20officers%20had%20to%20escape%20from%20the%20place%20of%20the%20incident%20without%20conducting%20search%20to%20save%20their%20lives%20as%20the%20mob%20became%20very%20violent%20and%20even%20chased%20the%20officials%20so%20as%20to%20deter%20the%20officials%20from%20performing%20their%20official%20duty%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Diabolical%20Move'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20T