in-q3-124010501263_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAbsence%20Of%20Law%20Can't%20Give%20Blanket%20Immunity%26quot%3B%3A%20High%20Court%20On%20Adultery%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20a%20law%20making%20adultery%20an%20offence%20cannot%20provide%20%26quot%3Bblanket%20immunity%26quot%3B%20to%20spouses%20in%20extramarital%20relationship%20and%20leave%20the%20victim%20individuals%20without%20a%20remedy%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20judgement%20released%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20high%20court%20said%20bigamy%20is%20an%20offence%20against%20conjugal%20right%20of%20the%20victim%20spouse%20and%2C%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20preference%20for%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20which%20is%20also%20recognised%2C%20due%20changing%20societal%20norms%2C%20law%20cannot%20be%20powerless%20against%20clandestine%20marriages%20and%20unions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Swarana%20Kanta%20Sharma%20said%20it%20was%20crucial%20to%20ensure%20legal%20protection%20for%20those%20who%20have%20committed%20to%20the%20sanctity%20and%20values%20of%20marriage%20and%20the%20requirement%20of%20proving%20a%20second%20marriage%20for%20the%20offence%20of%20bigamy%20was%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%20for%20society%20and%20for%20the%20victim%20spouse%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20people%20in%20today's%20era%20may%20or%20may%20not%20agree%20to%20the%20relevance%20of%20institution%20of%20marriage%2C%20but%20once%20legally%20married%2C%20the%20duty%20and%20the%20obligation%20by%20virtue%20of%20solemnization%20of%20marriage%20gives%20both%20the%20parties%20a%20new%20social%20and%20legal%20status%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20essence%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20law%20making%20adultery%20an%20offence%20cannot%20provide%20individuals%20with%20a%20blanket%20immunity..%20The%20Courts%20cannot%20afford%20to%20leave%20individuals%20without%20a%20legal%20remedy%2C%20especially%20those%20wives%20or%20husbands%20whose%20partners%20have%20entered%20into%20another%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20observation%20came%20while%20dealing%20with%20a%20case%20in%20which%20the%20husband%2C%20during%20the%20subsistence%20of%20his%20first%20marriage%2C%20allegedly%20lived%20as%20a%20married%20couple%20with%20another%20woman%20and%20even%20had%20a%20daughter%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20although%20individuals%20in%20live-in%20relationships%20were%20legally%20protected%2C%20such%20safeguards%20must%20not%20come%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20legal%20rights%20and%20protection%20afforded%20to%20spouses%20who%20are%20lawfully%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20recognizing%20and%20respecting%20the%20legal%20standing%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20and%20the%20individuals%20who%20opt%20for%20this%20lifestyle%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20that%20ensures%20legal%20protection%20for%20those%20who%20have%20committed%20to%20the%20sanctity%20and%20values%20of%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20stated%20that%20monogamy%20was%20a%20fundamental%20value%20and%20way%20of%20life%20under%20Hindu%20law%20and%2C%20while%20contemplating%20changes%20to%20legal%20frameworks%2C%20it%20was%20imperative%20to%20strike%20a%20delicate%20balance%20between%20upholding%20traditional%20values%20and%20responding%20to%20the%20evolving%20dynamics%20of%20contemporary%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20law%20cannot%20be%20powerless%20to%20stop%2C%20punish%20or%20limit%20clandestine%20marriages%20and%20unions%20when%20the%20first%20wife%20or%20husband%20are%20alive%20and%20the%20valid%20marriage%20subsists%2C%20as%20now%20a%20spouse%20performing%20a%20second%20clandestine%20marriage%20would%20not%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20punishment%20for%20adultery%20as%20it%20is%20no%20more%20an%20offence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20clandestine%20marriages%20are%20difficult%20to%20prove%20and%20the%20inability%20of%20a%20partner%20to%20prove%20performance%20of%20'saptapadi'%20(seven%20rounds%20around%20fire)%20by%20the%20other%20partner%20for%20the%20second%20marriage%20should%20not%20be%20exploited%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bclever%20tactic%20to%20circumvent%20the%20legal%20consequences%20of%20committing%20offence%20of%20bigamy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20absence%20of%20sufficient%20proof%20of%20second%20marriage%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Btravesty%20of%20justice%26quot%3B%20to%20let%20the%20husband%20escape%20liability%20towards%20the%20first%20wife%20and%20upheld%20the%20summons%20issued%20by%20the%20trial%20court%20to%20the%20husband%20for%20the%20alleged%20offence%20of%20bigamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20Court%20takes%20cognizance%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20inability%20of%20one%20partner%20to%20prove%20performance%20of%20saptapadi%20by%20the%20other%20partner%20while%20marrying%20for%20the%20second%20time%20during%20subsistence%20of%20first%20marriage%2C%20at%20the%20stage%20of%20summoning%20itself%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20other%20partner%20may%20have%20solemnized%20such%20marriage%20with%20the%20third%20person%20in%20secrecy%2C%20should%20not%20be%20exploited%20as%20a%20clever%20tactic%20to%20circumvent%20the%20legal%20consequences%20of%20committing%20offence%20of%20bigamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20legal%20proceedings%20do%20involve%20strategic%20elements%2C%20such%20smart%20maneuvers%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20compromise%20the%20principles%20of%20fairness%20and%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704474720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2