y%20be%20back%20on%20track%20soon%2C%20with%20the%20office%20of%20the%20lieutenant%20governor%20of%20Delhi%20informing%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20society%20running%20it%20has%20recently%20met%20and%20decided%20to%20release%20funds%20for%20its%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20appearing%20for%20the%20lieutenant%20governor's%20office%20told%20the%20court%20it%20was%20not%20a%20%26quot%3BCouncil%20of%20Ministers%20versus%20LG%26quot%3B%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20termed%20the%20case%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bstorm%20in%20a%20teacup%26quot%3B%20and%20told%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20B%20R%20Gavai%20and%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20that%20the%20LG%20is%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20scheme%20which%20was%20governed%20by%20a%20society%20headed%20by%20the%20city%20government's%20health%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20file%20an%20affidavit%20to%20that%20effect.%20If%20we%20find%20that%20the%20minister%20has%20taken%20us%20for%20a%20ride%2C%20we%20will%20impose%20exemplary%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20told%20senior%20advocate%20Sanjay%20Jain%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20LG's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJain%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNobody%20has%20taken%20anybody%20for%20a%20ride%20expect%20that%20the%20petitioner%20has%20used%20this%20court's%20forum%20to%20agitate%20something%E2%80%A6%20it%20is%20a%20classic%20case%20of%20storm%20in%20a%20teacup%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20bench%2C%20which%20was%20hearing%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20seeking%20release%20of%20funds%20for%20the%20scheme%2C%20that%20it%20was%20not%20a%20%26quot%3BCouncil%20of%20Ministers%20versus%20LG%26quot%3B%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20scheme%20was%20governed%20by%20a%20society%2C%20and%20in%20a%20recent%20meeting%20of%20the%20society%20which%20has%20taken%20place%20on%20January%202%2C%20they%20have%20decided%20to%20release%20the%20funds%20from%20which%20all%20pending%20claims%20will%20be%20issued%2C%26quot%3B%20Jain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20since%20the%20funds%20will%20be%20released%2C%20it%20will%20be%20the%20end%20of%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAsk%20the%20LG%20not%20to%20make%20every%20issue%20a%20prestige%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJain%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20LG%20is%20not%20involved%20in%20this.%20This%20is%20exactly%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20point%20out.%20It%20was%20a%20society%20which%20is%20headed%20by%20the%20health%20minister.%20It%20is%20the%20health%20minister%20only%20who%20took%20the%20meeting%20%E2%80%A6%20it%20is%20she%20only%20who%20has%20now%20released%20the%20funds%26quot%3B.%20The%20senior%20advocate%20said%20he%20was%20very%20surprised%20that%20the%20matter%20was%20brought%20before%20the%20court%20in%20this%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20asked%20him%20to%20file%20an%20affidavit%20within%20two%20weeks%20and%20adjourned%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%208%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20had%20sought%20responses%20from%20the%20office%20of%20the%20LG%20and%20others%20on%20the%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20had%20then%20submitted%20that%2023%2C000%20road%20accident%20victims%20have%20been%20provided%20cashless%20treatment%20in%20private%20hospitals%20under%20the%20'Farishtey%20Dilli%20Ke'%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Farishtey%20Dilli%20Ke'%20scheme%20encourages%20people%20to%20rescue%20road%20accident%20victims.%20Under%20the%20scheme%2C%20the%20government%20foots%20hospital%20bills%20of%20those%20who%20have%20met%20with%20accidents%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20sought%20immediate%20re-operationalisation%20of%20the%20scheme%20by%20clearing%20pending%20bills%2C%20releasing%20timely%20payment%20to%20private%20hospitals%20and%20initiating%20disciplinary%20ac