tor%20after%20a%20crew%20member%20allegedly%20snuck%20into%20her%20cabin%20and%20raped%20her%2C%20causing%20her%20to%20become%20pregnant.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20alleged%20assault%20occurred%20in%20May%202023%20aboard%20the%20Margaritaville%20at%20Sea%20Paradise%20as%20it%20was%20sailing%20from%20Rivera%20Beach%20in%20Florida%20to%20Freeport%2C%20Bahamas.%20The%20woman%2C%20identified%20as%20Jane%20Doe%2C%20filed%20a%20federal%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20cruise%20ship%20after%20the%20bartender%2C%20Hoobesh%20Kumar%20Dookhy%2C%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20sexually%20assaulting%20her%20cabin%20mate%20on%20the%20same%20night%20last%20May.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20obtained%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F01%2F04%2Fnews%2Fcruise-ship-passenger-claims-bartender-raped-impregnated-her%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPost%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ms%20Doe%20claimed%20that%20she%20and%20her%20cabin%20mate%2C%20identified%20as%20HB%2C%20had%20been%20drinking%20at%20a%20bar%20aboard%20the%20ship%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20May%205.%20Both%20charged%20the%20beverages%20to%20their%20cabin%2C%20%26quot%3Bproviding%20crewmembers%20staffing%20the%20bar%20access%20to%20their%20shared%20cabin%20number%20and%20room%20key%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20alleged%20that%20as%20they%20slept%20in%20the%20cabin%20later%20that%20night%2C%20the%20bartender%20entered%20the%20room%20and%20raped%20her.%20Ms%20Doe%20became%20pregnant%20as%20a%20result%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bforced%20to%20terminate%20the%20pregnancy%20from%20which%20she%20then%20suffered%20serious%20complications%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fcruise-ship-worker-raped-impregnated-passenger-lawsuit-1857671%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENewsweek%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ms%20Doe's%20attorney%2C%20Spencer%20Aronfeld%2C%20said%20that%20his%20client%20reported%20the%20assault%20to%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(FBI)%20prior%20to%20filing%20the%20lawsuit.%20She%20also%20did%20not%20undergo%20a%20paternity%20test%20to%20determine%20who%20impregnated%20her%20because%20she%20had%20not%20been%20sexually%20active%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20attorney%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20didn't%20need%20one%20since%20she%20knew%20she%20had%20not%20had%20sexual%20relations%20with%20anyone%20including%20her%20husband%20for%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20she%20has%20never%20had%20an%20abortion%20before-and%20she%20suffered%20vaginal%20clotting%20after%20the%20procedure.%20Under%20federal%20maritime%20law%20a%20cruise%20line%20is%20legally%20responsible%20anytime%20a%20crewmember%20rapes%20a%20passenger.%20There%20is%20no%20defense%20to%20an%20intentional%20harm%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Aronfeld%20told%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fat-least-10-patients-dead-after-us-nurse-allegedly-replaced-fentanyl-iv-bags-with-tap-water-4805621%5C%22%3EAt%20Least%2010%20Patients%20Dead%20After%20US%20Nurse%20Allegedly%20Replaced%20Fentanyl%20IV%20Bags%20With%20Tap%20Water%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Doe%20is%20now%20seeking%20more%20than%20%2475%2C000%20in%20damages%20from%20the%20cruise%20line.%20She%20told%20the%20FBI%20that%20she%20had%20been%20sleeping%20when%20she%20felt%20someone%20caressing%20her%20face.%20She%20woke%20and%20realised%20the%20person%20touching%20her%20was%20Dookhy.%20She%20told%20the%20federal%20agents%20that%20she%20tried%20to%20get%20the%20bartender%20to%20leave%20the%20cabin%2C%20but%20he%20moved%20to%20her%20cabin%20mate's%20bed%20and%20began%20to%20sexually%20assault%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Doe%20reported%20the%20incident%20to%20the%20ship%20security%20the%20next%20day.%20Officials%20then%20found%20the%20women's%20room%20key%20in%20the%20pocket%20of%20Dookhy's%20vest%20and%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20bartender%20touching%20HB's%20hand%20and%20face%20while%20she%20was%20asleep.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Ms%20Doe's%20cabin%20mate%20filed%20a%20separate%20lawsuit%20in%20August%20against%20Classica%20Cruise%20Operator%20Ltd%2C%20and%20against%20Margaritaville%20at%20Sea%2C%20alleging%20Dookhy%20also%20raped%20her.%20The%20bartender%20admitted%20to%20sexual%20intercourse%20with%20HB%2C%20however%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20encounter%20was%20consensual.%20He%20initially%20faced%20the%20possibility%20of%20life%20behind%20bars%20on%20a%20sexual-abuse%20charge.%20However%2C%20he%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20abusive%20sexual%20contact%20in%20October%20as%20part%20of%20a%20plea%20agreement%20that%20saw%20the%20more%20serious%20charge%20against%20him%20dropped.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDookhy%20now%20faces%20up%20to%20two%20years%20in%20prison%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20%24250%2C000%20at%20a%20sentencing%20hearing%20set%20for%20later%20in%20January.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704468780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-10%2Fp4ip2u7_cruise-generic_650x400_02_October_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-claims-cruise-ship-bartender-raped-and-impregnated-her-in-cabin-4806986%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20US%20woman%20is%20suing%20a%20cruise%20operator%20after%20a%20crew%20member%20allegedly%20snuck%20into%20her%20cabin%20and%20raped%20her%2C%20causing%20her%20to%20become%20pregnant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-claims-cruise-ship-bartender-raped-and-impregnated-her-in-cabin-4806986%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-woman-claims-cruise-ship-bartender-raped-and-impregnated-her-in-cabin-4806986%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%