%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-67895679.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Red%20Sea%20conflict%3A%20Agri%2C%20textile%20exporters%20hold%20back%20shipments%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704465759000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F26%2Ffull%2F1701016700-6372.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fthe-red-sea-conflict-agri-textile-exporters-hold-back-shipments-124010501125_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cost%20of%20freight%20and%20insurance%20has%20risen%20due%20to%20ships%20being%20compelled%20to%20avoid%20the%20region%20and%20take%20a%20longer%20route%20around%20the%20Cape%20of%20Good%20Hope%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fthe-red-sea-conflict-agri-textile-exporters-hold-back-shipments-124010501125_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fthe-red-sea-conflict-agri-textile-exporters-hold-back-shipments-124010501125_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fthe-red-sea-conflict-agri-textile-exporters-hold-back-shipments-124010501125_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Man%20Who%20Has%20Been%20Buying%20Dawood%20Ibrahim's%20Properties%20For%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20auction%20of%20four%20properties%20owned%20by%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%20concluded%20today%2C%20with%20two%20of%20the%20land%20parcels%20getting%20no%20bids%20and%20one%2C%20which%20had%20a%20reserve%20price%20of%20just%20Rs%2015%2C000%2C%20being%20sold%20for%20an%20eye-popping%20Rs%202%20crore.%20Dawood%20is%20India's%20most%20wanted%20terrorist%20and%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20hiding%20in%20Karachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20buyer%20of%20the%20plot%20said%20he%20paid%20so%20much%20for%20it%20because%20the%20survey%20number%20and%20the%20amount%20add%20up%20to%20a%20figure%20in%20numerology%20that%20works%20in%20his%20favour.%20He%20intends%20to%20set%20up%20a%20Sanatan%20school%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20tracts%20of%20agricultural%20land%20were%20auctioned%20under%20the%20Smugglers%20and%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Manipulators%20(Forfeiture%20of%20Property)%20Act%2C%201976.%20They%20are%20located%20in%20Mumbake%20village%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Ratnagiri%20district%2C%20and%20their%20combined%20reserve%20price%20was%20just%20Rs%2019.22%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20two%20bigger%20land%20parcels%20did%20not%20receive%20any%20bids%2C%20a%20plot%20with%20an%20area%20of%201%2C730%20sq%20m%20and%20a%20reserve%20price%20of%20Rs%201.56%20lakh%20was%20sold%20for%20Rs%203.28%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20smallest%20land%20parcel%2C%20which%20has%20an%20area%20of%20170.98%20sq%20m%20and%20had%20a%20reserve%20price%20of%20Rs%2015%2C440%2C%20has%20been%20sold%20for%20Rs%202.01%20crore.%20This%20plot%20was%20bought%20by%20lawyer%20Ajay%20Srivastava%2C%20who%20had%20earlier%20purchased%20three%20of%20the%20underworld%20don's%20properties%2C%20including%20his%20childhood%20home%20in%20the%20same%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20asked%20why%20he%20had%20paid%20so%20much%20for%20the%20agricultural%20plot%2C%20Mr%20Srivastava%2C%20who%20is%20a%20former%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20Sanatani%20Hindu%20and%20we%20follow%20our%20%3Cem%3Epanditji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20survey%20number%20(of%20the%20plot)%20and%20the%20amount%20have%20a%20figure%20that%20goes%20in%20my%20favour%20according%20to%20numerology.%20I%20will%20start%20a%20Sanatan%20school%20on%20this%20plot%20after%20getting%20it%20converted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20bid%20for%20Dawood%20Ibrahim's%20Bungalow%20in%202020.%20A%20Sanatan%20Dharm%20Pathshala%20Trust%20has%20been%20set%20up%20and%2C%20after%20getting%20it%20registered%2C%20I%20will%20start%20a%20Sanatan%20school%20there%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarlier%20Purchases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20auction%20of%20Dawood's%20properties%20was%20held%20in%202000%20and%20no%20one%20had%20turned%20up%20to%20bid%2C%20probably%20because%20of%20fear%20of%20the%201993%20Mumbai%20blasts%20mastermind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20auction%20in%20March%202001%2C%20in%20which%20Mr%20Srivastava%20was%20the%20only%20bidder%2C%20the%20lawyer%20had%20bought%20two%20shops%20owned%20by%20the%20terrorist%20in%20Mumbai's%20Nagpada.%20He%20is%20still%20fighting%20for%20possession%20of%20the%20shops%20even%20though%20a%20Mumbai%20court%20had%20ruled%20in%20his%20favour%20in%202011.%20The%20order%20was%20challenged%20in%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20and%20the%20case%20is%20being%20fought%20by%20the%20children%20of%20Dawood's%20sister%2C%20Haseena%20Parkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20auction%20in%202020%2C%20the%20lawyer%20bought%20Dawood's%20childhood%20home%20in%20Mumbake%20village%2C%20where%20the%20terrorist%20was%20born.%20He%20has%20not%20got%20the%20deed%20for%20the%20bungalow%20yet%2C%20because%20of%20some%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20documents%20which%20were%20prepared%20by%20a%20government%20department.%20The%20mistakes%20have%20now%20been%20corrected%20and%20he%20hopes%20to%20get%20the%20deed%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704465660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F5moufe78_dawood_625x300_20_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdawoods-plot-with-base-price-of-rs-15-000-sold-for-rs-2-crore-in-auction-4805802%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20auction%20of%20four%20properties%20owned%20by%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%20concluded%20today%2C%20with%20two%20of%20the%20land%20parcels%20getting%20no%20bids%20and%20one%2C%20which%20had%20a%20reserve%20price%20of%20just%20