0Bengaluru%20To%20Introduce%20Co-Education%20After%2075%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%2075%20years%20as%20a%20renowned%20women's%20college%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mount%20Carmel%20College%20is%20set%20to%20undergo%20a%20significant%20change.%20Starting%20from%20the%20upcoming%20academic%20year%2C%20the%20institution%20will%20become%20fully%20co-educational%2C%20with%20the%20management%20announcing%20the%20opening%20of%20all%20undergraduate%20and%20postgraduate%20programs%20to%20male%20students.%20However%2C%20the%20college%20management%20has%20not%20yet%20determined%20the%20percentage%20of%20seats%20reserved%20for%20boys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApplications%20are%20now%20invited%20from%20eligible%20students%20for%20the%20forthcoming%20academic%20year.%20While%20some%20postgraduate%20courses%20were%20made%20available%20to%20boys%20in%202015%2C%20this%20marks%20the%20first%20time%20that%20all%20courses%20will%20be%20open%20to%20them.%20The%20decision%20aligns%20with%20the%20university's%20aspirations%20to%20attain%20deemed%20university%20status.%20The%20announcement%20about%20the%20change%20was%20made%20following%20the%20celebration%20of%20its%20diamond%20jubilee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuma%20Singh%2C%20the%20college%20registrar%2C%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20diverse%20student%20body%2C%20citing%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20competition%20in%20a%20time%20when%20more%20women%20are%20entering%20the%20workforce.%20She%20highlighted%20the%20current%20need%20for%20a%20balance%20between%20male%20and%20female%20representation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollege%20registrar%20Suma%20Singh%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20have%20a%20diverse%20crowd%20because%20the%20competition%20element%20is%20very%20critical%2C%20as%20more%20women%20are%20joining%20the%20workforce%20and%20transition%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%20We%20are%20living%20in%20a%20time%20where%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20male-female%20balance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20female%20student%20expressed%20support%20for%20the%20change%2C%20stating%20that%20every%20university%20should%20have%20both%20genders%20for%20its%20unique%20advantages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20university%20now.%20Every%20university%20must%20have%20girls%20and%20boys%3B%20that's%20having%20its%20own%20advantage.%20It's%20good%20for%20a%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transition%20to%20a%20co-educational%20institution%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20gradual.%20The%20administration%2C%20contemplating%20this%20change%20for%20several%20years%2C%20recently%20solidified%20the%20decision%20during%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20registrar%20and%20deans.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704464700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fusa8av1o_mount-carmel-college-bengaluru_625x300_05_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fbengalurus-mount-carmel-college-to-admit-male-students-after-75-years-4806517%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Applications%20are%20now%20invited%20from%20eligible%20students%20for%20the%20upcoming%20academic%20year.%20The%20decision%20aligns%20with%20the%20university's%20aspirations%20to%20attain%20deemed%20university%20status.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fbengalurus-mount-carmel-college-to-admit-male-students-after-75-years-4806517%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fbengalurus-mount-carmel-college-to-admit-male-students-after-75-years-4806517%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fbengalurus-mount-carmel-college-to-admit-male-students-after-75-years-4806517%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22T20%20WC%202024%20Fixtures%20Revealed.%20India%20To%20Face%20Pakistan%20In%20New%20York%20On...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20T20%20World%20