%3A%22The%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20will%20begin%20on%20June%201%20and%20the%20much-anticipated%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20will%20be%20held%20on%20June%209%20in%20New%20York.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ft20-world-cup-2024-to-begin-on-june-1-india-to-face-pakistan-in-new-york-on-4806288%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ft20-world-cup-2024-to-begin-on-june-1-india-to-face-pakistan-in-new-york-on-4806288%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ft20-world-cup-2024-to-begin-on-june-1-india-to-face-pakistan-in-new-york-on-4806288%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Maestro'%3A%20Bradley%20Cooper's%20Biopic%20of%20Leonard%20Bernstein%20Examines%20the%20Man%20Trapped%20Under%20the%20Phenomenon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F05192303%2FEffect-58.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20throwaway%20scene%20in%20Bradley%20Cooper%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EMaestro%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20film%20built%20on%20the%20marriage%20of%20legendary%20musician%20and%20conductor%20Leonard%20Bernstein%20(Cooper)%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20actor%20Felicia%20Montealegre%20(Carey%20Mulligan)%20%E2%80%93%20we%20see%20the%20protagonist%20partaking%20in%20(what%20looks%20like)%20cocaine.%20He%20is%20surrounded%20by%20his%20manager%20and%20a%20student%2C%20who%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20hinted%2C%20is%20his%20lover.%20In%20the%20scene%2C%20as%20we%20see%20Bernstein%20not%20just%20taking%20drugs%20but%20also%20holding%20up%20the%20tray%20and%20serving%20his%20manager%20and%20the%20young%20man%2C%20what%20stands%20out%20is%20how%20bereft%20of%20judgement%20it%20all%20feels.%20The%20way%20the%20camera%20(by%20cinematographer%20Matthew%20Libatique)%20frames%20the%20three%20characters%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20clammy%2C%20crowded%20rave%2C%20the%20filmmaking%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20be%20casting%20aspersions%20on%20Bernstein.%20The%20scene%20is%20not%20preceded%20by%20overemphasising%20Bernstein%E2%80%99s%20inner%20turmoil%20(he%20had%20been%20living%20away%20from%20his%20wife%20and%20kids%20by%20then)%2C%20correlating%20his%20drug%20habit%20to%20it%2C%20and%20thereby%20%E2%80%98explaining%E2%80%99%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20sequence%20that%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20how%20clear-eyed%20Cooper%20is%20in%20%3Cem%3EMaestro%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20seeing%20the%20man%20trapped%20under%20the%20musical%20phenomenon%2C%20but%20also%20not%20trying%20to%20merely%20contain%20his%20life%20and%20legacy%20into%20a%20few%20words%2C%20scenes%2C%20and%20moments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECooper%20(who%20co-wrote%20the%20film%20with%20Josh%20Singer)%20realises%20the%20futility%20of%20simplifying%20and%20condensing%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20into%20a%20feature-length%20film%2C%20so%20he%20keeps%20alluding%20to%20events%20that%20took%20place%20in%20their%20life%20between%20the%20%E2%80%98scenes%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20film.%20As%20Leonard%20finds%20prominence%20and%20worldwide%20acceptance%20in%20his%20late%2030s%2C%20we%20see%20Felicia%20standing%20in%20the%20wings%20under%20his%20gargantuan%20shadow.%20When%20Leonard%20announces%20he%E2%80%99s%20completed%20writing%20a%20piece%20of%20score%20while%20being%20at%20home%20on%20holiday%20after%20a%20long%20world%20tour%2C%20Felicia%20quietly%20gets%20up%20from%20the%20living%20room%2C%20slips%20out%20of%20the%20window%20and%20jumps%20into%20the%20pool.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20whimsical%2C%20child-like%20action%2C%20but%20one%20that%20also%20conveys%20the%20suffocation%20she%E2%80%99s%20been%20feeling%20while%20being%20married%20to%20him%2C%20which%20has%20slowly%20built%20up%20over%20time.%20The%20scene%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20end%20there%3B%20the%20camera%20comes%20back%20to%20Leonard%E2%80%99s%20face%20who%20lets%20out%20a%20tiny%20laugh%20at%20Felicia%E2%80%99s%20incredulous%20reaction%2C%20only%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20all%20his%20actions%20that%20have%20driven%20her%20to%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgJP2QblqLA0%3Fsi%3DhvIaMfUXdOnmX_eP%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBradley%20Cooper%2C%20who%20announced%20himself%20as%20a%20first-rate%20director%20in%20his%20debut%2C%20%3Cem%3EA%20Star%20Is%20Born%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2018)%2C%20showcases%20his%20singular%20and%20precise%20directorial%20voice%20in%20%3Cem%3EMaestro%3C%2Fem%3E%20too.%20The%20early%20portions%20of%20Leonard%20and%20Felicia%E2%80%99s%20resemble%20a%20fairytale%20musical%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9850s%20%E2%80%93%20such%20is%20the%20sweeping%20scale%2C%20when%20things%20seem%20to%20be%20happening%20at%20a%20frightening%20pace.%20In%20an%20early%20scene%2C%20we%20see%20Leonard%20getting%20%3Cem%3Ethe%3C%2Fem%3E%20phone%20call%20to%20conduct%20with%20the%20New%20York%20Philharmonic%20Orchestra%20at%20the%20Carnegie%20Hall%20(after%20the%20original%20conductor%20falls%20ill)%20%E2%80%93%20and%20in%20one%20unbroken%20shot%2C%20he%20goes%20from%20his%20loft%20to%20the%20much-revered%20performance%20arena.%20Similarly%2C%20during%20Leonard%20and%20Felicia%E2%80%99s%20courtship%2C%20the%20film%20goes%20from%20their%20acquaintance-ship%20to%20him%20showcasing%20his%20musical%20theatre%20work%20to%20her%20in%20an%20inspired%20sequence.%20The%20sequence%20ends%20with%20white%20bed%20sheets%20flying%20over%20them%20on%20stage%2C%20to%20the%20bed%20sheet%20over%20their%20feet%20in%20one%20clean%20cut%20%E2%80%93%20telling%20us%20everything%20about%20their%20growing%20fondness%20and%20intimacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20once%20the%20marriage%20gets%20going%2C%20Libatique%E2%80%99s%20camera%20becomes%20less%20vivacious.%20It%20seems%20to%20be%20observing%20both%20Leonard%20and%20Felicia%2C%20staying%20on%20them%20for%20a%20few%20seconds%20longer%20after%20a%20%E2%80%98scene%E2%80%99%20has%20ended%20%E2%80%93%20documenting%20the%20unspoken%20feelings%20when%20they%20stopped%20paying%20attention%20to%20each%20other.%20Like%20most%20marriage%20stories%2C%20even%20this%20one%20has%20a%20stellar%20confrontation%20between%20Leonard%20and%20Felicia%2C%20when%20he%20comes%20home%20for%20a%20Thanksgiving%20dinner.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20raw%2C%20ruthless%20duel%20of%20words%2C%20impeccably%20performed%20by%20both%20Cooper%20and%20Mulligan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recurring%20complaint%20with%20Cooper%E2%80%99s%20film%20has%20been%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20focus%20on%20Bernstein%E2%80%99s%20musical%20exploits.%20To%20be%20the%20devil%E2%80%99s%20advocate%20here%2C%20instead%20of%20making%20a%20birth-to-death%20biopic%2C%20I%20can%20see%20why%20Cooper%20was%20dazzled%20by%20Leonard%20and%20Felicia%E2%80%99s%20love%20story%2C%20offering%20a%20more%20in-depth%20peek%20into%20the%20man%2C%20and%20helps%20us%20understand%20him%20better%2C%20than%20any%20montage%20of%20seeing%20him%20perform.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20bold%20choice%20%E2%80%93%20making%20a%20film%20on%20the%20life%20of%20a%20virtuoso%20%E2%80%93%20where%20his%20life%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20buried%20into%20the%20background%2C%20as%20his%20domestic%20quarrels%20rise%20to%20the%20fore.%20However%2C%20Cooper%20seems%20to%20know%20exactly%20the%20film%20he%E2%80%99s%20making%20and%20dives%20head-long%20into%20it%20with%20the%20same%20passion%20with%20which%20Bernstein%20would%20let%20the%20music%20flow%20through%20him%20while%20conducting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20is%20an%20exceptionally%20acted%20film%2C%20including%20the%20ancillary%20characters%20essayed%20by%20Matt%20Bomer%20and%20Maya%20Hawke%2C%20who%20plays%20his%20daughter%20Jamie.%20Most%20of%20these%20actors%20get%20that%20one%20scene%2C%20where%20they%20communicate%20their%20feelings%20without%20words.%20When%20Leonard%20introduces%20Felicia%20to%20David%20(Bomer)%20%E2%80%93%20his%20ex-lover%2C%20David%20looks%20at%20them%20with%20sorrow%20in%20his%20eyes%20and%20a%20smile%20on%20his%20face.%20Similarly%2C%20when%20Jamie%20is%20told%20to%20ignore%20the%20rumours%20about%20Leonard%20being%20involved%20with%20his%20younger%20students%2C%20you%20see%20her%20nodding%2C%20while%20also%20realising%20what%20kind%20of%20man%20her%20father%20really%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20too%20easy%20to%20say%20that%20Cooper%20means%20this%20film%20to%20be%20an%20acting%20showcase%20for%20himself%2C%20channelling%20Bernstein%E2%80%99s%20throaty%20voice%2C%20his%20relaxed%20body%20language%2C%20and%20a%20mind%20that%20could%20never%20stop%20racing%2C%20going%20through%20projects%2C%20performances%2C%20spouses%2C%20lovers%2C%20experiences%2C%20always%20anxious%20to%20get%20to%20the%20next%20thing.%20If%20anything%2C%20Cooper%E2%80%99s%20performance%20as%20Leonard%20Bernstein%20is%20the%20opposite%20of%20a%20vanity%20project.%20And%20we%20know%20this%20for%20how%20Cooper%20entrusts%20the%20stage%20to%20Mulligan%20in%20the%20second%20hour%2C%20making%20Felicia%20the%20protagonist%20of%20the%20film%2C%20as%20Leonard%20remains%20in%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20Mulligan%E2%80%99s%20deeply-affecting%20performance%20as%20Felicia%20that%20lies%20at%20the%20core%20of%20%3Cem%3EMaestro%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Mulligan%2C%20known%20for%20her%20stoic%20face%20while%20depicting%20total%20and%20complete%20devastation%20in%20films%20like%20%3Cem%3EAn%20Education%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2009)%2C%20%3Cem%3EWildlife%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2018)%2C%C2%A0%20employs%20it%20to%20great%20effect%20here%2C%20wordlessly%20conveying%20the%20humiliation%20of%20being%20wedded%20to%20a%20genius.%20Like%20in%20his%20directorial%20debut%2C%20Cooper%20seems%20smitten%20by%20the%20idea%20of%20unpacking%20the%20loneliness%20of%20icons%20and%20examining%20them%20for%20all%20their%20contradictions%2C%20transgressions%2C%20and%20what%20lights%20up%20their%20mind%20every%20morning.%20It%E2%80%99s%20fitting%20then%20that%20Cooper%E2%80%99s%20film%20becomes%20a%20tribute%20to%20Felicia%20%E2%80%93%20a%20choice%20Bernstein%20would%20have%20approved%20of%2C%20even%20if%20the%20film%20is%20named%20after%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704464346000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F05192303%2FEffect-58.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmaestro-bradley-coopers-biopic-of-leonard-bernstein-examines-the-man-trapped-under-phenomenon%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20actor-director%20makes%20the%20film%20equally%20about%20his%20wife%20and%20their%20troubled%20marriage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fmaestro-bradley-coopers-biopic-of-leonard-bernstein-examines-the-man-trapped-under-phenomenon%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20Senate%20Approves%20Resolution%20To%20Delay%20February%208%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Senate%20on%20Friday%20approved%20a%20resolution%20seeking%20a%20delay%20in%20the%20February%208%20general%20elections%20citing%20security%20concerns%2C%20the%20country's%20ARY%20News%20reported.%20The%20resolution%20presented%20by%20Senator%20Dilawar%20Khan%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20majority%20of%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20Information%20Minister%20Murtaza%20Solangi%20and%20PML-N%20Senator%20Afnan%20Ullah%2C%20who%20were%20present%20in%20the%20House%2C%20however%2C%20opposed%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20stated%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20upheld%20the%20right%20to%20vote%20for%20every%20citizen%20of%20Pakistan%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20was%20bound%20to%20conduct%20free%20and%20fair%20polls%20in%20contingent%20upon%20inclusivity%20and%20ensuring%20the%20participation%20of%20all%20regional%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20vote%20turnout%20in%20colder%20areas%20remains%20notably%20high%20during%20the%20moderate%20weather%20conditions.%20January%20and%20February%20are%20recognised%20as%20the%20coldest%20months%20in%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20areas%20in%20Balochistan%20and%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20stated%2C%20as%20per%20ARY%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20resolution%2C%20various%20political%20parties%20expressed%20their%20reservations%20regarding%20difficulties%20in%20ensuring%20participation%20in%20cold%20areas%20during%20the%20electoral%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecent%20attempts%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20JUI-F%20chief%20Fazlur%20Rehman%2C%20former%20lawmaker%20Mohsin%20Dawar%2C%20and%20other%20political%20figures%20had%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20political%20leaders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ministry%20of%20Interior%20has%20conveyed%20serious%20threats%20to%20the%20lives%20of%20prominent%20politicians%20increasing%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20political%20parties%20in%20exercising%20their%20right%20to%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20resolution%20noted%2C%20according%20to%20ARY%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20spike%20in%20attacks%20on%20security%20forces%20and%20citizens%2C%20particularly%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20and%20Balochistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Senate%20of%20Pakistan%20hereby%20resolves%20that%20the%20conduct%20in%20elections%20without%20addressing%20legitimate%20concerns%2C%20facilitating%20sufficient%20opportunities%20for%20election%20campaign%20and%20guaranteeing%20the%20safety%20of%20politicians%20and%20citizens%20would%20amount%20to%20violation%20of%20fundamental%20rights.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20election%20schedule%20may%20be%20postponed%20to%20facilitate%20the%20effective%20participation%20of%20people%20from%20all%20areas%20of%20Pakistan%20and%20belonging%20to%20all%20political%20shades%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20demanded%2C%20according%20to%20ARY%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704464160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-02%2Fpakistan-parliament_650x400_61456220597.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-senate-approves-resolution-to-delay-february-8-elections-4806451%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pakistan%20Senate%20on%20Friday%20approved%20a%20resolution%20seeking%20a%20delay%20in%20the%20February%208%20general%20elections%2C%20citing%20security%20concerns%2C%20Pakistan-based%20ARY%20News%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-senate-approves-resolution-to-delay-february-8-elections-4806451%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-senate-approves-resolution-to-delay-february-8-elections-4806451%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-senate-approves-resolution-to-delay-february-8-elections-4806451%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Troubled%20China%20shadow%20bank%20Zhongzhi%20files%20for%20bankruptcy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704463910000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106579987%2Cimgsize-2059947.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Ftroubled-china-shadow-bank-zhongzhi-files-for-bankruptcy%2Farticleshow%2F106577458.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%