d%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Tracxn%20report%2C%20India%20dropped%20to%20the%20fifth%20position%20in%202023%20among%20the%20highest-funded%20geographies%20globally.%20It%20had%20been%20ranked%20fourth%20in%20both%202022%20and%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20mature%20startups%20have%20been%20the%20most%20affected%20by%20the%20slowdown%2C%20as%20big-ticket%20investors%20such%20as%20Tiger%20Global%20and%20SoftBank%2C%20known%20for%20their%20aggressive%20deal-making%2C%20took%20a%20backseat.%20%E2%80%9CInvestors%20also%20took%20longer%20to%20write%20new%20cheques%2C%20turning%20cautious%20after%20questions%20were%20raised%20over%20corporate%20governance%20at%20several%20venture-backed%20startups%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704448815000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F05134407%2Fimage-1686.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Ffunding-for-indian-startups-hit-a-seven-year-low-in-the-december-quarter-of-2023-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20startups%20witnessed%20a%20nearly%2073%25%20decline%20in%20fundraising%20in%202023%2C%20raising%20%247%20billion%20as%20compared%20to%20%2425%20billion%20in%20the%20previous%20year%20%E2%80%93%20a%20significant%20drop%20from%20the%20funding%20recorded%20in%202022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Ffunding-for-indian-startups-hit-a-seven-year-low-in-the-december-quarter-of-2023-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBI%20to%20Probe%20Delhi%20Mohalla%20Clinics%20Over%20'Fake'%20Medical%20Tests%2C%20Corruption%20Allegations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F05152523%2FEffect-57.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Union%20home%20ministry%20has%20directed%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20to%20probe%20into%20the%20alleged%20scam%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20programme%20of%20Mohalla%20Clinics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20lieutenant%20governor%2C%20V.K.%20Saxena%2C%20just%20a%20day%20earlier%20had%20recommended%20that%20CBI%20launch%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20running%20of%20Mohalla%20Clinics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party-led%20Delhi%20government%20has%20been%20offering%20450%20medical%20tests%20free%20of%20cost%20to%20poor%20patients%20through%20its%20Mohalla%20Clinics%20initiative%20from%20January%201%2C%202023.%20Two%20private%20companies%20have%20been%20entrusted%20with%20the%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20allegations%20of%20fake%20tests%20and%20dummy%20patients.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CData%20clearly%20revealed%20that%20fake%20lab%20tests%20were%20carried%20out%20at%20these%20mohalla%20clinics%20that%20need%20to%20be%20further%20inquired%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20from%20the%20L-G%E2%80%99s%20office%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fhome-ministry-cbi-probe-delhi-mohalla-clinics-9096236%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Saxena%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20several%20disingenuous%20methods%20are%20being%20employed%20by%20the%20staff%20of%20Mohalla%20Clinics%20to%20get%20%E2%80%9Clakhs%20of%20tests%20conducted%20on%20dummy%20patients%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20government%20money%20is%20paid%20to%20private%20firms%20as%20per%20an%20inquiry%20by%20the%20Vigilance%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaxena%E2%80%99s%20office%20said%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20only%20the%20digit%20%E2%80%9C0%E2%80%9D%20was%20entered%20in%20the%20section%20meant%20for%20mobile%20numbers%20in%2011%2C657%20cases%3B%20the%20space%20was%20left%20blank%20in%208%2C251%20cases%3B%20mobile%20numbers%20of%203%2C092%20patients%20were%20entered%20as%209999999999%3B%20400%20mobile%20numbers%20began%20with%201%2C2%2C3%2C4%20or%205%3B%20and%20the%20same%20number%20was%20used%20more%20than%2015%20times%20in%20around%20a%20thousand%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20Vigilance%20department%20report%2C%20Saxena%E2%80%99s%20office%20said%20as%20many%20as%2020%2C000%20tests%20were%20recommended%20by%20the%20outsourced%20labs%20either%20on%20blank%20mobile%20numbers%20or%20on%20%E2%80%9C0%E2%80%9D%20digit.%20According%20to%20LG%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cscam%E2%80%9D%20runs%20into%20hundreds%20of%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20alleged%20scam%20first%20became%20public%20in%20September%20last%20year%20after%20it%20emerged%20that%20some%20doctors%20and%20staff%20of%20seven%20Mohalla%20Clinics%20in%20Southwest%2C%20Shahdara%2C%20and%20Northeast%20districts%20were%20employing%20dubious%20means%20to%20mark%20their%20attendance%20through%20pre-recorded%20videos.%20Those%20doctors%20were%20later%20removed%20from%20the%20empanelment%20of%20doctors%20and%20a%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Delhi%20health%20minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20said%20he%20had%20received%20complaints%20against%20a%20few%20doctors%20coming%20late%20or%20leaving%20early%20from%20work.%20He%20had%20ordered%20action%20against%20them%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704448700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F05152523%2FEffect-57.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcbi-to-probe-delhi-mohalla-clinics-over-fake-medical-tests-corruption-allegations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20home%20ministry%20ordered%20the%20probe%20a%20day%20after%20Delhi%20LG%20recommended%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20matter%2C%20accusing%20authorities%20of%20using%20disingenuous%20met