%E2%80%9Cinformed%20source.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoleimani%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20US%20drone%20attack%20at%20Baghdad%20airport%20in%202020.%20He%20was%20a%20high-ranking%20official%20in%20the%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%C2%A0(IRGC)%20and%20in%20command%20of%20the%20elite%20Quds%20Force%2C%20responsible%20for%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%E2%80%99s%20campaigns%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20observed%20a%20day%20of%20mourning%20on%20Thursday%2C%20and%20authorities%20have%20also%20called%20for%20mass%20protests%20on%20Friday%20when%20the%20funerals%20of%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20blasts%20will%20be%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIran%20vows%20revenge%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20%E2%80%9CIS%E2%80%9D%20claimed%20responsibility%2C%20Iranian%20President%20Ebrahim%20Raisi%20condemned%20the%20%E2%80%9Cheinous%20and%20inhumane%20crime%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20top%20authority%2C%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ayatollah%20Khamenei%2C%20vowed%20revenge%20for%20the%20twin%20bombings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIranian%20leader%20vows%20%E2%80%98harsh%20response%E2%80%99%20after%20twin%20blasts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20tabindex%3D%5C%22-1%5C%22%20data-duration%3D%5C%2201%3A53%5C%22%20data-play-btn-title%3D%5C%22Play%20video%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cpicture%20tabindex%3D%5C%22-1%5C%22%3EEarlier%2C%20Iran%20expert%20at%20United%20Against%20Nuclear%20Iran%2C%20Kasra%20Aarabi%2C%20told%20DW%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20attack%20itself%20certainly%20has%20all%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20ISIS%20operations%20in%20Iran.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fpicture%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20would%20suit%20the%20government%20in%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20likely%20that%20the%20regime%20will%20blame%20ISIS%20that%20will%20enable%20the%20%5BIslamic%2