F2023%2F06%2F09154147%2Fmodi-school.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20education%20ministry%20on%20Thursday%20(January%204)%20launched%20a%20portal%20with%20details%20of%20the%20programme%20under%20which%20students%20from%20across%20the%20country%20will%20visit%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20school%20in%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Vadnagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20from%20class%209-12%20will%20be%20required%20to%20register%20on%20the%20portal%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20programme%20named%20%E2%80%9CPrerana%E2%80%9D.%20Applicants%20will%20then%20go%20through%20a%20three-stage%20selection%20process%20which%20will%20involve%20activities%20like%20recording%20a%20short%20video%2C%20writing%20essays%2Fpoems%2Fstories%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20creative%20expression%20on%20topics%20like%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20should%20I%20be%20selected%20for%20Prerana%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9CMy%20Vision%20of%20India%20%40%202047%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-launches-portal-for-students-to-register-for-tour-to-pm-s-school-in-guj-101704395102273.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20students%20from%20each%20district%20will%20be%20selected%20in%20batches%20of%2020%20%E2%80%93%2010%20girls%20and%2010%20boys%20%E2%80%93%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20programme%20which%20will%20last%20for%20at%20least%20a%20year%20according%20to%20the%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202022%2C%20the%20government%20announced%20its%20plan%20to%20launch%20Prerana%20to%20inspire%20the%20youth%20to%20become%20%E2%80%9Ccatalysts%20of%20change%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ministry%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrerana%3A%20An%20Experiential%20Learning%20program%E2%80%9D%20aims%20to%20offer%20a%20meaningful%2C%20unique%2C%20and%20inspiring%20experience%20to%20all%20participants%2C%20and%20empowering%20them%20with%