3Cspan%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Eric%20Trump%2C%20the%20former%20president%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20said%20in%20an%20email%20that%20the%20Chinese%20bank%20mentioned%20in%20the%20report%20had%20signed%20a%2020-year%20lease%20at%20Trump%20Tower%20in%202008%2C%20almost%20a%20decade%20before%20his%20father%20took%20office.%20And%20he%20argued%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20the%20former%20president%20had%20not%20allowed%20his%20personal%20business%20incentives%20to%20drive%20his%20official%20actions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20report%2C%20Eric%20reiterated%20on%20his%20social%20media%20account%20that%20any%20profit%20that%20the%20business%20earned%20during%20the%20presidency%20were%20sent%20to%20the%20US%20Treasury%20through%20a%20voluntary%20annual%20payment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704438658000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F05123915%2FScreenshot-2024-01-05-at-12.38.4.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fdonald-trump-businesses-india-presidency%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20spent%20a%20total%20of%20%24282%2C764%20at%20Trump%20World%20Tower%20in%20New%20York%20and%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%20in%20the%20US%20capital%20of%20Washington%20D.C.%20from%202017%20to%202020.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fdonald-trump-businesses-india-presidency%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22B-1%20bomber%20crashes%20at%20South%20Dakota%20Air%20Force%20base%2C%20crew%20ejects%20safely%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704436922000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106566011%2Cimgsize-1195344.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fb-1-bomber-crashes-at-south-dakota-air-force-base-crew-ejects-safely%